      },
      "options": {
        "content": "# 🧪 Pruebas de Rendimiento - TodoMercado API\n\nEste tablero muestra el comportamiento de la API bajo diferentes niveles de carga.\nLos colores indican: 🟢 Saludable | 🟡 Precaución | 🔴 Crítico\n\n**Test: $test_name | Latencia: P99**\n\n| Test | Usuarios | Tipo | Descripción |\n|------|----------|------|-------------|\n| 01_smoke | 1 VU | 🧪 Smoke | Verificar endpoints básicos |\n| 02_load_50 | **50 VUs** | 🚦 Load | Carga media sostenida |\n| 03_load_200 | 200 VUs | 📈 Load | Carga alta sostenida |\n| 04_stress_500 | 500 VUs | 🔥 Stress | Punto de quiebre |\n| 05_spike | Spike | 💥 Spike | Picos repentinos |\n| 06_soak_200 | 200 VUs | 💧 Soak | Resistencia prolongada |",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "13.1.0",
      "transparent": true
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "gauge",
      "title": "Disponibilidad",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "13.1.0",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 3
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 90
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 95
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "100 * (1 - sum(k6_http_reqs_total{testid=\"$test_name\", expected_response=\"false\"}) / sum(k6_http_reqs_total{testid=\"$test_name\"}))",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "disponibilidad"
        }
      ]
    },
